snippet.textDisplay: Totally appreciate the diversity in what coke studio bangla is trying to do. But i think it’s too early to compose jazz music as it targets a very niche audience. Initially we should be showcasing our traditional folk songs and maybe next season or the season after you can start trying new things. There are so many beautiful songs that we are waiting for. Kachar bhetor ochin pakhi, ore nil doriya. These are the songs we want you to create magic with! Please compose these songs!
snippet.textOriginal: Totally appreciate the diversity in what coke studio bangla is trying to do. But i think it’s too early to compose jazz music as it targets a very niche audience. Initially we should be showcasing our traditional folk songs and maybe next season or the season after you can start trying new things. There are so many beautiful songs that we are waiting for. Kachar bhetor ochin pakhi, ore nil doriya. These are the songs we want you to create magic with! Please compose these songs!
